><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>O método&nbsp;<strong><code>Node.cloneNode()</code></strong>&nbsp;duplica um&nbsp;elemento node (nó)&nbsp;da estrutura de um documento&nbsp;DOM. Ele retorna um clone do elemento para o qual foi invocado.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em><var>dupNode</var></em> = <em><var>node</var></em>.cloneNode(<em><var>deep</var></em>);\n</pre>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"node\"><em>node</em></dt>\n <dd>O elemento node (nó) a ser clonado 'duplicado'.</dd>\n <dt id=\"dupnode\"><em>dupNode</em></dt>\n <dd>O novo elemento node (nó) resultado da clonagem do elemento node.</dd>\n <dt id=\"deep_optional_1\"><em>deep <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span> [1]</em></dt>\n <dd>true se os elementos filhos do nó que está sendo clonado devem ser clonados juntos, ou false para clonar apenas o nó&nbsp;específico dispensando, assim, qualquer elemento DOM filho. Veja os exemplos abaixo.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>Nota:</strong>&nbsp;Na especificação do&nbsp;DOM4 (implementado no&nbsp;Gecko&nbsp;13.0 (Firefox 13 / Thunderbird 13 / SeaMonkey 2.10)), o argumento&nbsp;<code>deep</code>&nbsp;é opcional. Se omitido, por padrão, o método age como se o valor de deep fosse setado como true durante a sua execução. &nbsp;&nbsp;Para criação de clones superficiais, o argumento&nbsp;<code>deep</code> deve ser setado como&nbsp;<code>false</code>.</p>\n\n<p>Este comportamento foi alterado na última especificação. Se omitido o argumento deep, o método irá interpretar o valor de deep como se fosse false. Embora ele continue opcional, é recomendado que você sempre observe o argumento deep para fins de compatibilidade anterior e posterior. Com o Gecko 28.0&nbsp;(Firefox 28 / Thunderbird 28 / SeaMonkey 2.25 / Firefox OS 1.3)), foi advertido aos desenvolvedores para não omitirem o argumento. Iniciado com o Gecko 29.0&nbsp;(Firefox 29 / Thunderbird 29 / SeaMonkey 2.26)), um clone superficial é o padrão ao invés de um clone aprofundado.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"paragrafos\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>Texto parágrafo<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//Obtém o elemento div</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> div_p <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"paragrafos\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//Obtém o primeiro filho do elemento div</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> p <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> div_p<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>firstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//Clona o elemento, no caso, um parágrafo</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> p_clone <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> p<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">cloneNode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//Adiciona o clone do elemento &lt;p&gt; ao elemento &lt;div&gt;</span>\ndiv_p<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">appendChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>p_clone<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notas","title":"Notas","isH3":false,"content":"<p>A clonagem&nbsp;de um elemento node copia todos os seus atributos e valores. Porém, não tem o mesmo comportamento em relação aos \"event listeners\".</p>\n\n<p>O elmento node resultante da ação de clonagem não faz parte da estruturam DOM do documento até que ele seja adicionado utilizando o método appendChild() ou outro similar, conforme exemplo acima.</p>\n\n<p>Se o argumento&nbsp;(deep) for setado como false, os nós filhos do elemento node clonado não serão clonados juntos, assim como os respectivos&nbsp;textos.</p>\n\n<p>Se o argumento (deep) for setado como true, os nós filhos, toda a árvore DOM do elemento clonado, será clonada junto.</p>\n\n<div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect3\"><strong>Cuidado:</strong> <code>cloneNode()</code>&nbsp;pode duplicar&nbsp;IDs em um documento.</div>\n\n<p>Se o elemento node (nó) clonado&nbsp;tiver uma ID e o novo elemento node resultante da clonagem for ser inserido no mesmo documento, a ID de um dos nós deve ser alterada para que observem o princípio de unicidade. Em outras palavras, um mesmo documento não pode ter elementos com IDs iguais. Se for o caso de trabalhar com manipulação de elementos DOM através do atributo \"name\", tome cuidado em observá-lo.</p>\n\n<p>Clonagem de&nbsp;node (nó) &nbsp;para um documento diferente, use o seguinte método:&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document/importNode\"><code>Document.importNode()</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specificações","title":"Specificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentários</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-node-clonenode\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Node.cloneNode()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Core/core.html#ID-3A0ED0A4\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 3 Core Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Node.cloneNode()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-3A0ED0A4\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Core Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Node.cloneNode()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n   <td>Definição Inicial</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect4\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect5\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect6\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>(deep)</code>&nbsp;como parâmetro opcional</td>\n   <td>\n    <p><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span><sup>[1]</sup></p>\n   </td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/13\" title=\"Released on 2012-06-05.\">13.0</a> (13.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>\n    <p><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span><sup>[1]</sup></p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>(deep)</code>&nbsp;como parâmetro opcional</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>13.0 (13.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Valor padrão para o argumento&nbsp;(<code>deep)</code>&nbsp;é&nbsp;<code>false</code>.</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Notas","id":"notas"},{"text":"Specificações","id":"specificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"O método Node.cloneNode() duplica um elemento node (nó) da estrutura de um documento DOM. Ele retorna um clone do elemento para o qual foi invocado.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.cloneNode","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Node.cloneNode()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Node.cloneNode()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.cloneNode","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.cloneNode()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Node.cloneNode()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"element.cloneNode","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Node.cloneNode()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.cloneNode","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Node.cloneNode()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/node/clonenode","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/node/clonenode/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node","title":"Node"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node/cloneNode","title":"Node.cloneNode()"}],"pageTitle":"Node.cloneNode() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}